", raw)\n\t}\n}\n\nfunc TestValidateLongUrl_LoopbackIP(t *testing.T) {\n\terr := businesslogic.ValidateLongUrl(\"http://127.0.0.1/evil\")\n\trequire.Error(t, err)\n\tassert.ErrorIs(t, err, businesslogic.ErrValidation)\n}\n\nfunc TestValidateLongUrl_IPv6Loopback(t *testing.T) {\n\terr := businesslogic.ValidateLongUrl(\"http://[::1]/evil\")\n\trequire.Error(t, err)\n\tassert.ErrorIs(t, err, businesslogic.ErrValidation)\n}\n\nfunc TestValidateLongUrl_PrivateIP_RFC1918(t *testing.T) {\n\tfor _, raw := range []string{\n\t\t\"http://10.0.0.1\",\n\t\t\"http://192.168.1.1\",\n\t\t\"http://172.16.0.1\",\n\t\t\"http://172.31.255.255\",\n\t} {\n\t\terr := businesslogic.ValidateLongUrl(raw)\n\t\trequire.Error(t, err, \"URL: %s\", raw)\n\t\tassert.ErrorIs(t, err, businesslogic.ErrValidation, \"URL: %s\", raw)\n\t}\n}\n\nfunc TestValidateLongUrl_PublicIP_Valid(t *testing.T) {\n\t// 8.8.8.8 is a public IP address (Google DNS)\n\tassert.NoError(t, businesslogic.ValidateLongUrl(\"https://8.8.8.8\"))\n}\n","filePath":"/home/alexl70/src/pet/linkshortener/backend/business-logic/url_validator_test.go"},"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01W186RCfUpny9whUt4gBtES__vscode-1773574791514","cwd":"/home/alexl70/src/pet/linkshortener"}

